        <heading>2822.  Requirements of affidavit evidence</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2822.  Requirements of affidavit evidence
The affidavits referred to in Article 2821 shall be executed by two persons having knowledge of the facts sworn to.  These affidavits shall be filed in the record of the succession proceeding.</p>
        </content>
